00:10:14.250 --> 00:10:18.370
But I just recently got a
teaching job at a university

00:10:18.370 --> 00:10:20.690
in the University of York.

00:10:20.690 --> 00:10:23.760
And it happens to be
right beside Eyam.

00:10:23.760 --> 00:10:25.060
&gt;&gt; Wow.

00:10:25.060 --> 00:10:29.380
&gt;&gt; So I could even live there now.

00:10:29.380 --> 00:10:32.180
&gt;&gt; Wow. Five more pieces.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:38.460
You know, one thing and we can,
