00:10:55.910 --> 00:11:00.050
And the Chirino is the
vibrato breath or [inaudible].

00:11:00.050 --> 00:11:01.930
Yeah, yeah.

00:11:01.930 --> 00:11:06.930
But there's this real sense of
I don't know, I get the sense

00:11:06.930 --> 00:11:11.380
of a breathing entity on stage.

