And you've also done other
Mahler projects as well.

00:14:46.890 --> 00:14:54.100
&gt;&gt; Yeah, that's actually, Mahler
is a, is an obsession and I,

00:14:54.100 --> 00:14:58.780
I feel as a conductor I do a lot of
you know, Beethoven, Bach, Mozart,

00:14:58.780 --> 00:15:03.420
Tschaikovsky all canonical works,
