It's from you know, if it's
Bach, it's Lutheran Germany,

00:15:22.610 --> 00:15:27.560
if it's I don't know, Beethoven
it's from Vienna in 18th

00:15:27.560 --> 00:15:29.010
and 19th Century and so forth.

