And a lot of that music is
emblematic of that time.

00:15:33.450 --> 00:15:35.030
Some of it's very religious or some

00:15:35.030 --> 00:15:38.700 position:56%
of it reflects post
enlightenment feelings and you know,

00:15:38.700 --> 00:15:41.000 position:56%
it's a very, very different context.

