to be performance.

00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:08.670
Maybe I felt teaching
but now when I look back,

00:33:08.670 --> 00:33:11.470
before that it makes sense that
I would want to be a composer,

00:33:11.470 --> 00:33:16.620 position:56%
because I've always been
interested in sound I've always kind

00:33:16.620 --> 00:33:20.290
