telling me something.

00:33:20.290 --> 00:33:25.680
I've never seen like music as just
music or just kind of pure sound,

00:33:25.680 --> 00:33:31.020
it's always been something
kind of narrative to me.

00:33:31.020 --> 00:33:35.940
So it kind, it makes sense even
though it was something I only

00:33:35.940 --> 00:33:38.930
discovered when I was maybe 19 so.

